HAI 1.3
I HAS A a ITZ 1
I HAS A b ITZ 2
I HAS A result ITZ 2

IM IN YR loop
  b R SUM OF a AN b
  a R DIFF OF b AN a
  BOTH SAEM 0 AN MOD OF b AN 2, O RLY?
    YA RLY
      result R SUM OF result AN b
  OIC

  DIFFRINT b AN SMALLR OF b AN 4000000, O RLY?
    YA RLY
      GTFO
  OIC
IM OUTTA YR loop

VISIBLE "Result: " result

KTHXBYE
